'''Albert Einstein''' ([[Tet-ngî]]: Albert Einstein, 1879-ngièn 3-ngie̍t 14-ngit－1955-ngièn 4-ngie̍t 18-ngit), ngi-sṳ̍p sṳ-ki [[Yù-thai-ngìn|Yù-thai]] heu-yí lî-lun [[Vu̍t-lî ho̍k-kâ]], chhóng-li̍p [[Siông-tui-lun]], hien-thoi [[Vu̍t-lî-ho̍k]] ke lióng-thai chṳ̂-chhû chṳ̂-yit. Sûi-yèn Einstein ke chṳt-nèn fông-chhàng-sṳt  '''E = mc2''' chui chho̍k-miàng, kì yîn-vi "tui lî-lun vu̍t-lî ke kung-hien, thi̍t-phe̍t he fat-hien kông-thien háu-yin" yì-yèn tet-tó 1921-ngièn Nobel Vu̍t-lî-ho̍k chióng. Einstein chúng-khiung fat-péu sâm-pak tô phiên [[khô-ho̍k]] lun-vùn lâu yit-pak ńg-sṳ̍p-phiên fî-khô-ho̍k chok-phín. Einstein pûn chhṳ̂n-cho he "hien-thoi vu̍t-lî ho̍k chṳ̂ fu" khi̍p ngi-sṳ̍p sṳ-ki sṳ-kie chui chhung-yeu [[khô-ho̍k-kâ]] chṳ̂-yit. 

==Ke-ngìn sên-fa̍t==
Einstein yî 1879-ngièn 3-ngie̍t 14-ngit chhut-sên chhai [[Tet-koet Ti-koet]] chṳ̂ [[Württemberg Vòng-koet]] [[Ulm-sṳ]]. Kì ke fu-chhîn Hermann Einstein he yit-miàng sông-ngìn. Kì ke mû-chhîn Pauline Kochhe yit-vi [[Yîm-ngo̍k-kâ]]. Einstein yit-kâ mò chûn-sùn [[Yù-thai-kau]] kûi-kí ke [[Yù-thai-ngìn]]. 

